e. You did? Was she Bee-ish? - A wasp?! Your parents will kill you! - No, no, no, not a wasp. - Spider? - I\'m not attracted to spiders. I know it\'s the hottest thing, with the eight legs and all. I can\'t get by that face. So who is she? She\'s... human. No, no. That\'s a bee law. You wouldn\'t break a bee law.', '2023-01-14 15:32:01', 0);
